text: Jacqueline Bisset (born 13 September 1944) is an English actress. She has appeared in a lot of notable movies. She played Jackie in Two for the Road in 1967 (which also starred Audrey Hepburn). Bisset also played Miss Goodthighs in Casino Royale, another 1967 movie. She has also appeared on television. ==Early life== Bisset was born in Weybridge, Surrey, England. She was brought up in Reading, Berkshire, where she lived in the suburb of Tilehurst.
